pageContext.claim: “Hey, Obama made a deal for a book. Is that running a business? I'm sure he didn't even discuss it while he was president, yeah. He has a deal with Netflix. When did they start talking about that? That’s only, you know, a couple of examples.”
pageContext.analysis: In defending the Doral deal, Trump mentions deals that Obama arranged after he left office, speculating without evidence that Obama started negotiating them when he was president.
